snippet.title: Max's Tales - Trailer
snippet.description:
Max's Tales is a 2D Platformer Game inspired by Super Mario Games.  

The characters Max and Lummy face several enemies that arrived to threaten the world, commanded by a powerful wizard.

It's a 2 player coop game, enjoy.

It’s recommended to play with controllers.

ALPHA VERSION.

A Demo version will be released soon.

Links do Play
Itch io: https://jonathanprado.itch.io/maxs-tales
NewGrounds: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/879795
